OpenU IL Theme and Accordion Topics Course Format
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

----------------------------------------------------
Description
----------------------------------------------------

Enclosed are two interconnected projects:

1. A Moodle theme designed by OpenU IL (see screenshot).
2. A Moodle course format "accordion topics" which allows the topics to be minimized and maximized.


----------------------------------------------------
Installation Information
----------------------------------------------------

1. Copy "ouil" directory to moodle/course/format.
2. Copy "ouilBlue" directory to moodle/theme.
3. After you have copied the files you may choose this theme from inside Moodle.



